ActBudget Implementation Act, 2019, No. 1
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day on Which this Order is Published as the Day on Which Subdivision H of Division 9 of Part 4 of that Act Comes into Force
PrecisOrder fixing the day on which this Order is published in the Canada Gazette, Part II, as the day on which Subdivision H of Division 9 of Part 4 of the BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2019, No. 1, chapter 29 of the Statutes of Canada, which received royal assent on June 21, 2019, COMES INTO FORCE, other than sections 206 to 212, which came into force on assent.
